=== Recommendations ===
1. If no serial devices found, enable UART with: sudo raspi-config
2. Go to Interface Options → Serial → Enable
3. If permission denied, add user to dialout group
4. Common working devices on Pi: /dev/ttyAMA0, /dev/serial0
5. For USB serial adapters: /dev/ttyUSB0

